# Telecom Customer Churn Dashboard (Tableau)

📊 This project visualizes churn patterns in the telecom industry using Tableau. Built as part of the Visual Analytics course (MAX 507) at Illinois Institute of Technology.

## 🔍 Objective
To identify key drivers of customer churn and provide actionable insights to stakeholders using dynamic dashboards.

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Tableau
- Excel (for data prep)
- Calculated Fields, Set Actions, Parameters

## 📈 Key Insights
- Customers without international plans had a **71.2% churn rate**.
- Month-to-month contract holders had the highest churn.
- High data usage and multiple lines also contributed to increased churn risk.

